content: Hello Jeyachandran, welcome to the technical round of our interview. I'm Master, your hiring officer for the Software Engineer position at Google. I'll be going through your resume and asking you questions based on your skills and experiences. Please feel free to ask me any clarifying questions, but for now, I'll start by asking about your development experience. Can you tell me more about your experience with React.js and Node.js while working at Fabromant?
i completed the react js and node js project sir

Can you walk me through your project and what kind of features you built using React.js and Node.js? For example, what type of authentication did you implement, or any specific challenges you faced during development?
